.sentryclirc
.env.sentry-build-plugin

# Local-only launch/security audit docs — never publish to the public repo
AUDIT_REPORT.md
IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md
FAST-SOCIO-LaunchReadiness.md
# These three name real people. The incident report and the DAST identify
# students by roll number (i232064, i245681) and the owner by personal email,
# alongside the attacker's IP and coordinates; the DAST is marked "Confidential
# — For Internal Use Only" and its Appendix C JWT carries its author's address.
# The hardening plan is a live inventory of still-open weaknesses. This repo is
# public, so committing any of them publishes that permanently — history, forks
# and mirrors survive a later delete.
FAST-SOCIO-SecurityHardening-Plan.md
SECURITY-INCIDENT-2026-07-15.md
vapt_report.md

